title: Star Trek GO Fonts JB Patch
creator: star-E

extendedInfo.description: //////Jelly Bean (Android 4.1 and above) must also install the 'Star Trek GO Fonts JB Patch'  to get it properly installed.//////Click below on 'More by star-E' to find it. It must be done AFTER installing this app to set the directories in which the assets will be installed. Sorry for the inconvenience....but it's still better than in-app purchasing.//////After installing don't press 'Open'. Also, don't use the shortcut icon GO Launcher creates.//////To apply the fonts, open the settings of the apps, scan for fonts, then select the one you like. Also, check the screenshots in the Play Store for visual directions.Enjoy the fonts of Star Trek on your phone. These fonts will complete the look of the 'New Star Trek' themes made by star-E or any of the other nice Star Trek themes out there. You can also use it just as is with any theme to give it a nicer look. These fonts install for:-GO Launcher-GO SMS Pro-GO Keyboard  *only the New Star Trek font for GO Keyboard*Although it is meant for the 'GO' apps, the fonts are also discoverable by most other apps that can scan for fonts.### Unless you are rooted, you will not be able to use these fonts as your default font/system font on your phone. ###Also, make sure to scan for the fonts in each app and apply them. Check the screenshots for visual directions.Included fonts:-Enterprise               (all upper case)-LCARS                   (all upper case)-New Star Trek         (all upper case)-New Star Trek Bold  (all upper case)-Star Trek TOS title-Star Trek Film Voyager DS9 title-Star Trek TNG title-Klingon Script-Romulan Falcon-Klingon      (alien/unreadable)-Romulan    (alien/unreadable)-Vulcan       (alien/unreadable)*The (alien/unreadable) fonts could be fun to set as contact names since you can see their pictures anyways. They may also be used for extra privacy, or if you can remember 10 characters, a fun clock font.Also look for:New Star Trek Go Launcher ThemeNew Star Trek GO Contacts ThemeNew Star Trek Go Locker ThemeNew Star Trek GOWidget ThemeNew Star Trek Go SMS ThemeNew Star Trek GO Keyboard ThemeNew Star Trek Live WallpaperNew Star Trek GO FontsNew Star Trek clock & battery skin (available free in Beautiful Widgets theme picker)*clock updated to v2*To get informed when I release new Star Trek themes, follow me on twitter. @SethSteen or Facebook http://www.facebook.com/new.star.trek.theme Also, if you're a Trekkie I would appreciate it if you could support my work by clicking 'g+1' or sharing it on your social networks.If you like my work, PLEASE leave me a nice review to help me continue. Too many people never read the directions and leave a bad review saying, "It doesn't work".*If you are having trouble and the contact developer link isn't working, please contact me at seththomaslewis@gmail.com That is my personal email so I can get notifications right away and offer the fastest support.

reviews.title: NST Theme Suit Review
reviews.comment: Hey everyone, I have to say that this is an epically cool suite of themes you can download. They are amazingly aesthetically pleasing and they function really well. I love how you can customize the entire phone to be wholegrain NST awesome-sauce! Additionally, Seth (the creator) has amazing customer service. I\'ve had some questions here and there about settings and the like and he is on the reply immediately. Absolutely wonderful customer service, I couldn\'t be happier. I\'ll be paying attention for additional theme options,specifically hoping for a soundboard option from Seth. Thanks! Rob
